rmp.university: University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill
comments: The thing about Prof. Tibbo is that she really doesn't seem to care about her students.  She doesn't answer direct questions, her assignments are unclear and ill-timed.  Her syllabus is ridiculous. She seems more concerned with her professional standing than her teaching.
